private boolean useDefaultWildCards
        Deprecated. Use attribute rules instead
        Use default settings for wildcard searching when searching Strings. If false no wildcards ("%") are added for the search and an exact match is required

      • orderBy

        private java.lang.String orderBy
        orderBy - Specify one of these to order the results:
        • AdminSearch.ORDER_BY_LASTNAME_ASCENDING
        • AdminSearch.ORDER_BY_LASTNAME_DESCENDING
        • AdminSearch.ORDER_BY_ID_ASCENDING (the default)
        • AdminSearch.ORDER_BY_ID_DESCENDING

      • formatAddresses

        private boolean formatAddresses
        When set, the formattedAddress attribute of the Address objects is populated. The default value is false.
